---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Concepts & Ascents and the writer behind it."
>
  <article class="about">
    <h1 class="essay-title">About</h1>

    <hr class="essay-rule" />

    <div class="essay-body">
      <p>
        <em>Concepts &amp; Ascents</em> is a venue for short essays at the
        intersection of metaphysics, philosophy of religion, and the
        contemplative traditions. The questions taken up here are old: the
        structure of reality, the relation of unity to multiplicity, the soul's
        ascent to the One, and the long conversation between Greek philosophy
        and the revealed traditions that drew it forward. The center of
        gravity is the Neoplatonic and Akbarian lineages.
      </p>

      <p>
        It is written by Rashad Abdulsalam, based in Florida.
      </p>

      <p>
        The aim is to organize a body of thought slowly, in public, in writing
        that is precise rather than ornamented. Essays appear when the writing
        is ready.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p class="contact">
        Correspondence is welcome at <a href="mailto:hello@conceptsandascents.com"
          >hello@conceptsandascents.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about .contact {
    text-indent: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
